拿不到指纹  尸体消失了
Couldn't get them. The body's gone.

473
00:22:46,460 --> 00:22:47,230
什么
What?

474
00:22:47,240 --> 00:22:49,320
已经在停尸间找了45分钟
Searched that morgue for 45 minutes.

475
00:22:49,600 --> 00:22:51,960
