-有新消息  -能等等吗  芬奇
- I have news. - Can it wait, Finch?

502
00:24:26,410 --> 00:24:28,150
我破解了李的加密邮件
I've cracked Lee's encrypted emails.

503
00:24:28,150 --> 00:24:30,980
是情报  汇报给他父亲
They're messages, reporting back to his father,

504
